Package gw.cc.question.entity

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Answer
    Answer Text, Logical and Numeric Answers supplied in a specific Question Set.
    AnswerDelegate
    AnswerDelegate Text, Logical and Numeric Answers supplied in a specific Question Set.
    AnswerSet
    AnswerSet This is a set of answers that correspond to the user filling out one question set form
    Question
    Question A Question for ClaimCenter
    QuestionChoice
    QuestionChoice One choice in the set of choices for a question of type Choice
    QuestionFilter
    QuestionFilter A filter for this question set that must pass in order for the question to be displayed in the UI.
    QuestionSet
    QuestionSet A set of questions for ClaimCenter
    QuestionSetFilter
    QuestionSetFilter A filter that controls the visiility of the question set based on the answer to a given question.
    SIUAnswerSet
    SIUAnswerSet Join table between the answer set and the claim, to allow for multiple SIU answer sets on the same claim
    SubQuestion
    SubQuestion A piece of text to be displayed in a bulleted list bellow a question.
